{"tid":1833050,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃子華套《乜代宗師》都唔睇 點對得住前線手足！","createTime":"2020-01-21T14:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T13:43:36.000Z","uid":149371,"like":19,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca41e4c6a2910398664d6f95bd1fcf53a392ddf5","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"子華拍埋電影Gchi✨✊🏼光復香港您地都5睇<br />\n<br />\n您地對5對得住一眾推拉c日日咁辛苦開電腦抗爭呀<br />\n<br />\n見D人話子華扮黃賺錢真系好嬲囉！💔🌊<br />\n<br />\n我就準備叫DADDY出錢包場請埋D FD睇嫁啦🤙🏼  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇子華 撐黃色經濟圈<br />\n💛✊🏼</span>"},{"pid":"449b22ea60a3245ef4fc2402f86620e3c17ebea8","tid":1833050,"uid":139173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"Ching好波<br />\n子華放下手段難得拍比香港人睇<br />\n我決定約埋班藍絲一齊大和解睇戲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d490ae32abed30597dcd954a5b9f3b1fcb0af3a3","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"449b22ea60a3245ef4fc2402f86620e3c17ebea8","tid":1833050,"uid":139173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"Ching好波<br />\n子華放下手段難得拍比香港人睇<br />\n我決定約埋班藍絲一齊大和解睇戲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"冇錯，就算佢係假黃都要撐，因為電影圈點都要搵個黃色代表。袋住先，唔好再深究黃藍💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"cba8ff2abccdafa6b0d3e7adadd190a02738130b","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"先唔評論黃子華係咪真黃，但睇佢MV已經知佢想外界認為佢係黃，呢個正正就係黃色經濟圈嘅威力，越多人願意為香港市場表態，就越可以擴大黃色經濟圈，尤其如果呢套戲因為表態紅咗，我相信一定有其他人跟風💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"a419629b568e2b3d7f3ff62cb9590de8fe761356","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"不停響度挑釁引發批鬥嘅係怕黃色經濟圈嘅5毛<br />\n睇唔睇戲係自己選擇💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"b67bf4d58fa3fc8c5e377f77b538189e6b326c1f","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"唔知成班五毛定00後喺出面帶風向話黃子華食兩家 佢都畀人封殺咗 仲點食兩家💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"3fd3fbf568a18184d4cf4cdbaef8abc9ec5ecd42","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"黃子華話佢套戲想拍比香港人睇<br />\n咁香港人去睇返<br />\n支持香港電影有咩問題？<br />\n如果華狗話呢套戲係黃色經濟圈<br />\n最後套戲大賣 再次反映到香港市場幾強<br />\n吸引更多電影人願意關注返本土<br />\n我地有咩損失 <br />\n反華點解要咁緊張<br />\n理性討論下💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"d2d0a8223373374009e339d9b49d902101b799ac","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢黃，起碼佢姓黃。唔好問啦，黃色經濟圈只係做俾人睇，唔好太認真深究黃藍💛✊🏼"},{"pid":"c7a1eb5ffadb3df473e0f6fefa9c1f5cb3bd663e","tid":1833050,"uid":132174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"好大仇口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad34e17d256674ffb16c4d9e5e2ea167a1117ca","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Gchi💛✊🏼<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>子華✨🤙🏼</span>"},{"pid":"542a3e31b3544e40a48af73421775a15a1a24f05","tid":1833050,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"小心此人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZ0-Y6loPRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTZ0-Y6loPRo&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=a4b8c093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZ0-Y6loPRo</a>"},{"pid":"7760728bc22c88a00b3cf1600e63a1424e278fde","tid":1833050,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a1eb5ffadb3df473e0f6f